#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:2
msgid "QTensor"
msgstr "QTensor"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :mod:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor` module defines the "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` class and related helpers for "
"representing and manipulating quantum states and operators in sparse "
"form."
msgstr ""
"El mòdul :mod:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor` defineix la classe "
":class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` i funcions auxiliars relacionades "
"per representar i manipular estats quàntics i operadors en forma "
"dispersa."

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:8
msgid ""
"The :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` wraps a dense NumPy array or "
"SciPy sparse matrix into a CSR-format sparse matrix, and can represent:"
msgstr ""
"El :class:`~qilisdk.core.qtensor.QTensor` embolcalla un array dens de "
"NumPy o una matriu dispersa de SciPy en una matriu dispersa en format "
"CSR, i pot representar:"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:10
msgid "**Kets** (column vectors of shape ``(2**N, 1)``)"
msgstr "**Kets** (vectors columna de forma ``(2**N, 1)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:11
msgid "**Bras** (row vectors of shape ``(1, 2**N)``)"
msgstr "**Bras** (vectors fila de forma ``(1, 2**N)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Operators / Density Matrices** (square matrices of shape ``(2**N, "
"2**N)``)"
msgstr ""
"**Operadors / Matrius de densitat** (matrius quadrades de forma ``(2**N, "
"2**N)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:13
msgid "**Scalars** (``(1, 1)`` matrices)"
msgstr "**Escalars** (matrius ``(1, 1)``)"

#: ../../modules/core/core_qtensor.rst:15
msgid "Examples of creating various quantum objects:"
msgstr "Exemples de creació de diversos objectes quàntics:"

